org.beryx.streamplify.partperm

Class BigIntegerPartialPermutations

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beryx.streamplify.BigIntegerIndexedSpliterator<int[],BigIntegerPartialPermutations>
      • org.beryx.streamplify.partperm.BigIntegerPartialPermutations
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Spliterator<int[]>, Streamable<int[],BigIntegerPartialPermutations>

    public class BigIntegerPartialPermutations
extends BigIntegerIndexedSpliterator<int[],BigIntegerPartialPermutations>
    Provides streams of partial permutations.
    For permutations with a length <= 18, you may consider using the more efficient LongPartialPermutations.
